    "uen": "202602440M",
    "description": "<p>Altwood Design is a newly established interior design firm founded by a <strong>Red Dot Design Award–winning designer</strong>, strategically located in Singapore’s city centre along <strong>Robinson Road</strong>.</p><p>We specialise in <strong>high-end, large-scale interior design and renovation</strong>, serving mainly <strong>luxury residential</strong> <strong>projects</strong>. Backed by an established industry network and a proven track record in delivering <strong>complex, large-format projects in more than 17 years</strong>, our team brings together strong design vision, technical expertise, and refined execution.</p><p>As a growing studio, we are building a team of <strong>young, motivated, and eager-to-learn talents</strong> who aspire to develop their craft at the highest level. Our <strong>Head of Design works closely with the team</strong>, providing <strong>hands-on mentorship and personal coaching</strong>, ensuring meaningful professional growth and exposure to premium projects.</p><p>At Altwood Design, we believe in cultivating designers who not only create beautiful spaces, but also understand concept development, materiality, detailing, and real-world execution.</p>",
